Malo *sunca* je sve što mi treba. (A little bit of sun is all I need.)

U ovoj čaršiji ima *malo* trgovina. (There are few shops in this bazaar.)

Nastavićeš da radiš kada ti se za to *malo* plati? (Will you continue to work when you get paid so little?)

Za *malu* sumu novca možeš da dobiješ mnogo. (For a small amount of money you can get a lot.)

Ne treba *malom* detetu da se daju teške knjige. (It's not necessary to give heavy books to a small child.)